Package edu.cnm.deepdive.irt.hikethrough.entities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Inventory
    Public class for storing inventory items using ormlite.
    InventoryType
    Unused Inventory Type class
    Level
    Level class that defines the terrain for each level using the method defined in GameView class.
    Level.Tile
    Location class "Tile" to determine where the map tiles begin to be place and iterate in a spiral fashion creating a hexagon-shaped map
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MapTileType
    Enumerator class that defines a selection of map tiles with specific weights with respect to their placement on the map and costs to be calculated when Dijkstras Movement class is defined.
